General.Name: Binero Group AB
General.Description: Binero Group AB (publ) provides cloud and digital infrastructure services for companies and organizations in Sweden. The company offers public cloud services; Kubernetes, a container platform provides OKD solutions; graphics card acceleration for machine learning and AI-based processing of large data; data storage and security services; and software and managed cloud services, as well as IT consultancy services. It also operates colocation datacenters; and OpenShift container platform. The company was formerly known as Oniva Online Group Europe AB (publ) and changed its name to Binero Group AB (publ) in June 2018. Binero Group AB (publ) was incorporated in 1985 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
